WEBVTT

00:01.504 --> 00:02.753
We hear you've been on ditching school.

00:02.839 --> 00:05.589
I wanna drop out. I got a job at that bar.

00:05.675 --> 00:08.092
- Come to California with me.
- You're on your own path.

00:08.144 --> 00:09.343
I think what you really need

00:09.429 --> 00:10.728
is to do this on your own.

00:10.763 --> 00:12.596
- They wanna book the tour.
- I'll call you every night.

00:12.648 --> 00:15.266
(Elizabeth) I'll answer every night.

00:15.318 --> 00:17.768
(Carter) I have been
hanging out at Jared's.

00:17.820 --> 00:19.937
- He's way too old for you.
- You're 17?

00:20.022 --> 00:22.940
Did you know he's married?

00:23.025 --> 00:24.492
- Seriously?
- You think I enjoy

00:24.577 --> 00:25.659
rifling through your underwear drawer

00:25.745 --> 00:27.278
looking for the money that you owe me?

00:27.363 --> 00:29.113
I'm gonna have some
stuff for you to do soon.

00:29.198 --> 00:30.364
I want you to leave.

00:30.450 --> 00:31.665
You can't sell drugs at my party.

00:31.751 --> 00:33.451
Carter, something's wrong with Seth!

00:33.503 --> 00:34.952
Come on, hey. Hey!

00:35.037 --> 00:36.954
No, no, no. He's dead.

00:37.006 --> 00:38.038
We got into this together.

00:38.124 --> 00:39.423
We'll get out of it together too.

00:39.459 --> 00:41.258
Your friend says he knew
drugs were being sold.

00:41.294 --> 00:42.626
I don't believe you.

00:42.712 --> 00:43.844
Carter's in trouble.

00:43.930 --> 00:44.962
My dad's getting out.

00:45.047 --> 00:46.680
Hey, son.

00:46.766 --> 00:48.966
No! No!

00:49.018 --> 00:50.634
You should think about moving near me.

00:50.686 --> 00:52.436
You're kinda the greatest son ever.

00:52.472 --> 00:54.271
You know I would do the same thing for you.

00:54.307 --> 00:55.773
- Bird?
- I'm pregnant.

00:55.808 --> 00:57.641
Okay, we're gonna figure this out.

00:57.727 --> 00:59.143
Carter's in a lot of trouble

00:59.228 --> 01:01.312
and she's gonna need
all the help she can get.

01:01.364 --> 01:02.530
Hey! Lori!

01:02.615 --> 01:04.482
Give me one reason not to kill you.

01:04.534 --> 01:05.983
She didn't know anything about the drugs.

01:06.035 --> 01:07.318
<i>- I admit it.
- That's it.</i>

01:08.788 --> 01:11.739
I'm sorry, I thought I
had it all under control.

01:11.824 --> 01:14.158
I will always be there for you.

01:14.243 --> 01:15.543
Thank you.

