01:25.438 --> 01:29.173
♪♪

01:35.681 --> 01:38.349
- Carter.
- Hey.

01:38.401 --> 01:40.518
What the hell are you doing here?

01:40.570 --> 01:42.236
My lawyer got me out on bail.

01:42.321 --> 01:44.355
Can I talk to you for a minute?

01:44.407 --> 01:46.156
I don't think we have
anything to talk about.

01:46.192 --> 01:47.441
- Carter, please...
- What are you doing?

01:47.527 --> 01:48.993
There's a few things
I just need to explain.

01:49.028 --> 01:50.578
Yeah, I'll bet, like why you threw me

01:50.663 --> 01:52.112
under the bus with the cops.

01:52.198 --> 01:53.998
I didn't... I mean,
yeah, I did, but I knew

01:54.033 --> 01:55.249
you'd get off, okay? You're underage.

01:55.334 --> 01:58.369
Really? That's your explanation?

02:00.122 --> 02:03.207
Wow, thank you, that's very noble of you.

02:03.292 --> 02:04.542
I have no excuse, okay?

02:04.627 --> 02:06.510
Except I have my little girl to support.

02:06.546 --> 02:07.678
I can't go to jail.

02:07.713 --> 02:09.797
And to hell with everyone else, right?

02:09.882 --> 02:11.215
No, no, it's not what I'm saying.

02:11.267 --> 02:14.184
I was in way over my head,
things got out of control.

02:14.220 --> 02:15.386
- Oh, my God.
- Please, Carter,

02:15.471 --> 02:16.770
you gotta listen to me, okay?

02:16.856 --> 02:18.389
I'm not asking you to forgive me.

02:18.441 --> 02:20.107
But after everything
that went down between us,

02:20.192 --> 02:21.525
can't you just hear me out?

02:21.561 --> 02:24.228
Fine. Explain.

02:24.280 --> 02:26.146
I was in the hole before I met you,

02:26.232 --> 02:27.698
I was about to lose the bar.

02:27.733 --> 02:29.233
- Yep, you told me that.
- What you don't know

02:29.285 --> 02:30.985
is that I borrowed money from some guys

02:31.070 --> 02:32.319
to help dig myself out.

02:32.405 --> 02:34.038
They seemed okay, I thought I was on my way

02:34.073 --> 02:35.122
to paying them off because the money

02:35.207 --> 02:36.373
we were making from the parties.

02:36.409 --> 02:37.741
But then they started charging me more,

02:37.793 --> 02:39.960
twisting my arm and forcing me to do stuff.

02:40.046 --> 02:41.829
So, you started dealing for them,

02:41.914 --> 02:44.131
and you made Ben do it too.

02:44.216 --> 02:45.833
Look, I know I should've stood up to them,

02:45.918 --> 02:47.217
but they threatened me.

02:47.253 --> 02:49.470
They said they were
gonna hurt my little girl.

02:49.555 --> 02:51.922
I just want you to know
that if I could go back,

02:52.008 --> 02:53.424
I would do it all differently.

02:55.061 --> 02:56.427
I still love you, Carter.

02:56.479 --> 02:58.512
I need you to know that.

02:58.598 --> 03:00.481
And if there's any way
you could just give me

03:00.566 --> 03:02.266
another chance.

03:05.021 --> 03:06.437
I gotta go, Jared.

03:11.327 --> 03:13.277
♪ There you go ♪

03:13.329 --> 03:16.196
♪ There you stay ♪

03:16.282 --> 03:18.115
♪ Keeping low ♪

03:18.167 --> 03:20.451
♪ Never want to play ♪

03:20.536 --> 03:23.120
♪ You've been up and down, down ♪

03:23.172 --> 03:26.123
♪ You've been low, low, low ♪

03:26.175 --> 03:30.928
♪ Pretending to not feel alone ♪

03:30.963 --> 03:33.939
♪ Pretending to not feel alone ♪

03:34.039 --> 03:36.145
